{"id": "anc_expand_push", "modality": "animations", "name": "Expand Push", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a horizontal row of FOUR equal-width cards centered on screen. Over ~3s the SECOND card smoothly expands to about double width while the third and fourth cards slide right to make room (the row stays centered as a group). All cards stay on the same row and fully on screen.", "requirements": ["All four cards stay fully within the viewport at every frame (none pushed off the right edge)", "The second card visibly widens over time", "Cards never overlap each other during the push", "All four cards remain on a single aligned row (shared vertical center) throughout", "The third and fourth cards visibly shift right as the second expands", "No scrollbar appears at any frame"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 5, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2136, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 11853}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 10, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2242, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 11435}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2079, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 11847}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_expand_push_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_expand_push_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Expansion Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .card-container {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 24px;\n            animation: containerCenter 3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            height: 400px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: width 3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .card-1, .card-3, .card-4 {\n            width: 280px;\n        }\n\n        .card-2 {\n            width: 280px;\n            animation: expandCard 3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card-icon {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 36px;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .card-1 .card-icon {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);\n        }\n\n        .card-2 .card-icon {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4ecdc4, #44a08d);\n        }\n\n        .card-3 .card-icon {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #45b7d1, #96c93d);\n        }\n\n        .card-4 .card-icon {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb, #f5576c);\n        }\n\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .card-description {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #7f8c8d;\n            text-align: center;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .card-2 .card-description {\n            animation: fadeInContent 3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .expanded-content {\n            opacity: 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            animation: fadeInExpanded 3s ease-in-out 1.5s forwards;\n        }\n\n        .expanded-content h3 {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .expanded-content p {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #7f8c8d;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes expandCard {\n            0% {\n                width: 280px;\n            }\n            100% {\n                width: 560px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeInContent {\n            0%, 50% {\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n            100% {\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeInExpanded {\n            0% {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            100% {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes containerCenter {\n            0% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"card-container\">\n        <div class=\"card card-1\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">1</div>\n            <h2 class=\"card-title\">Analytics</h2>\n            <p class=\"card-description\">Track your performance with detailed insights and metrics.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"card card-2\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">2</div>\n            <h2 class=\"card-title\">Dashboard</h2>\n            <p class=\"card-description\">Comprehensive overview of all your projects and tasks in one place.</p>\n            <div class=\"expanded-content\">\n                <h3>Advanced Features</h3>\n                <p>Real-time collaboration, custom workflows, automated reporting, and intelligent notifications to keep your team synchronized and productive.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"card card-3\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">3</div>\n            <h2 class=\"card-title\">Reports</h2>\n            <p class=\"card-description\">Generate comprehensive reports and export data seamlessly.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"card card-4\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">4</div>\n            <h2 class=\"card-title\">Settings</h2>\n            <p class=\"card-description\">Customize your workspace and manage user preferences.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Expansion Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .card-container {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 24px;\n            animation: containerShift 3s ease-in-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            height: 400px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            transition: all 3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .card::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            height: 4px;\n            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\n        }\n\n        .card-1 {\n            width: 280px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);\n        }\n\n        .card-1::before {\n            background: #c44569;\n        }\n\n        .card-2 {\n            width: 280px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4834d4, #686de0);\n            animation: expandCard 3s ease-in-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card-2::before {\n            background: #30336b;\n        }\n\n        .card-3 {\n            width: 280px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d2d3, #54a0ff);\n            animation: slideRight 3s ease-in-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card-3::before {\n            background: #2f3542;\n        }\n\n        .card-4 {\n            width: 280px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5f27cd, #a55eea);\n            animation: slideRight 3s ease-in-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card-4::before {\n            background: #341f97;\n        }\n\n        .card-icon {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            font-size: 36px;\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .card-subtitle {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            text-align: center;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n        }\n\n        .card-2 .card-content {\n            animation: fadeInContent 3s ease-in-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card-extra-content {\n            opacity: 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            animation: fadeInExtra 3s ease-in-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .card-extra-content p {\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .card-button {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 24px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card-button:hover {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes expandCard {\n            0% {\n                width: 280px;\n            }\n            100% {\n                width: 560px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideRight {\n            0% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: translateX(280px);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes containerShift {\n            0% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: translateX(-140px);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeInExtra {\n            0% {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            60% {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            100% {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"card-container\">\n        <div class=\"card card-1\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83d\udcca</div>\n            <div class=\"card-title\">Analytics</div>\n            <div class=\"card-subtitle\">Track your performance</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"card card-2\">\n            <div class=\"card-content\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83d\ude80</div>\n                <div class=\"card-title\">Growth</div>\n                <div class=\"card-subtitle\">Accelerate your business</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card-extra-content\">\n                <p>Unlock powerful insights and drive exponential growth with our comprehensive suite of tools designed for modern businesses.</p>\n                <button class=\"card-button\">Learn More</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"card card-3\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83c\udfaf</div>\n            <div class=\"card-title\">Strategy</div>\n            <div class=\"card-subtitle\">Plan your success</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"card card-4\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83d\udca1</div>\n            <div class=\"card-title\">Innovation</div>\n            <div class=\"card-subtitle\">Stay ahead of trends</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}